headline: Unum Group Q4 Earnings and Revenues Miss Estimates, Premiums Rise Y/Y
summary: UNM Q4 earnings and revenues miss estimates as segment profits fall, but premiums rise 2% year over year amid higher benefits and expenses.

headline: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish on Aflac Stock?
summary: As Aflac has lagged the S&P 500 over the past year, Wall Street analysts remain cautious on the stock, reflecting tempered expectations for its near-term performance and growth outlook.

headline: Aflac Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
